{"tid":1224102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]係件事完結之前每日出街都戴口罩","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T12:14:54.000Z","uid":35854,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3329b240e4ece70e2ba7758199308fa6cd6a91","tid":1224102,"uid":35854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:03:01.000Z","msg":"幾個好處<br />\n<br />\n1. 防止細菌傳播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 保護做緊野既人<br />\n當戴口罩既人愈多，做野既人既風險就愈細<br />\n<br />\n3. 維持士氣<br />\n宜家無左一個聚集既地方，其實好難維持士氣，亦都無可能無啦啦係條街叫口號。<br />\n簡簡單單戴個口罩等大家知道身邊係有同路人<br />\n<br />\n4. 容易參與<br />\n鍾意可以叫埋d姨媽姑姐叔伯兄弟一齊參與 壯大聲勢<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6ce6cc34acdbeca094e0bb2cd1d08c1b360605","tid":1224102,"uid":35854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cc20a499d81a8450dc210407142f691df26de1","tid":1224102,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d268f13f1ff91ecc42fa1fbaf30b13e9da6d2f62","tid":1224102,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"到時先算啦屌 撤都未撤諗完結"},{"pid":"45333f4233ee7ff040156b4d1748a264374d10c5","tid":1224102,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d268f13f1ff91ecc42fa1fbaf30b13e9da6d2f62","tid":1224102,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"到時先算啦屌 撤都未撤諗完結"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:18:52.000Z","msg":"「完結之前」！"},{"pid":"7bcfb639dbfb34ca7216520c8628f6524893776b","tid":1224102,"uid":71458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:20:21.000Z","msg"